Fuel efficiency ratings for three types of oil heaters

Data for Exercise 10.32

Format

A data frame with 30 observations on the following 6 variables.

TypeA
a numeric vector
TypeB
a numeric vector
TypeC
a numeric vector
Rating
a numeric vector
Type
a numeric vector
Ranks
a numeric vector

References

Kitchens, L. J. (2003) Basic Statistics and Data Analysis. Duxbury
